{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"How-to guides","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Howto","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/About\">關於 MDN</a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>貢獻 MDN</summary>\n            <ol>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Getting_started\">開始入門 MDN</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute\">貢獻 MDN</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Howto\">Things you can do</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Localize\">Localizing MDN</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Guidelines\">MDN 內容與風格指南</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Structures\">Content structures</a></li>\n             </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>這些文章將會帶領你一步步完成貢獻 MDN 專案所需完成的目標</p><div class=\"row topicpage-table\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <div class=\"section\" id=\"sect2\"><dl><dl><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"how_to_properly_tag_pages\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Howto/Tag\">How to properly tag pages</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\"><strong>Article tags</strong> are an important way to put visitors in touch with helpful content. Each page should normally have several tags to help keep content organized. This page explains the best way to tag pages so that our readers can find information and we can keep ourselves organized.</dd></dl></dl></div>\n    <div class=\"section\" id=\"sect3\"><dl><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"編輯以及新增頁面\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Howto/Create_and_edit_pages\">編輯以及新增頁面</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\">幾乎每位 MDN 的貢獻者在 MDN 中都會做的兩件基本工作，即為編輯一個已存在的頁面或者是新增一個頁面。這篇文章將介紹如何編輯文件的基本技能。</dd></dl></div>\n    </div>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"這些文章將會帶領你一步步完成貢獻 MDN 專案所需完成的目標","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"How-to Leitfäden","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"MDN web docs: How-to guides","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Guías prácticas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Guides \"Comment faire\"","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"MDN web docs: How-to ガイド","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"MDN web docs 사용 방법","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"How-to guides","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Guia de contribuição","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Руководства \"Как сделать\"","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"MDN 使用指南","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/mdn/contribute/howto","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/mdn/contribute/howto/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/MDN","title":"MDN 專案"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute","title":"貢獻 MDN"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Howto","title":"How-to guides"}],"pageTitle":"How-to guides - MDN 專案 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}